data.message: **Welcome to the GolmiEval Task!** Describe the highlighted piece on the board on the right so that another person could **uniquely** identify it.
If you're not sure which piece is the target, just click on it! If that's your target, I'll tell you so.
Once you're ready you can simply send your description with the chat on the bottom. You will see a total of 15 boards
Here's a little help: you can reference pieces according to this legend
The piece looks like a big T and is red.
The piece is gray and looks like a small z. Its close to another of the same shape and more or less in the middle.
the piece is surrounded by many other pieces. Its green and looks like P but its turned.
This looks like U but in green.
Looks like P but in blue.
This looks like Z and its lilac.
This is the red T at the top.
This is a W in gray in the middle.
This is like a x. In lilac. Most at the top.
This is shaped like the N. Its blue and at the right.
Still 5 boards to go. You almost made it!

Its orange. Shaped like the N and in the right touching a gray X.
